## 策略公式样例

### Long 策略
```
ADA_1h_初熊: ((ABS(supertrend) - linreg_slope(16)) < stoch_d)
BNB_1h_初熊: ((stoch_d > cmo(24)) AND (cmo(16) > fvg_detect))
ETH_COIN_1h_牛: (((adx(32) > ema(163)) AND (bb_upper < fisher_transform(13)))...)
```

### Short 策略
```
ADA_1h_盘整: ((MIN(macd_hist, close) + MIN(...)) < ...)
DOT_1h_熊: ((bop >= ((ABS((klinger * MIN(cci(12), volume_momentum(12))))...)
SOL_1h_熊: (-(ABS((MAX(-(sma(101)), chaikin_osc) + demand_index(8)))) > ...)
```

策略复杂度不等，从简单的 2 指标比较到复杂的嵌套 IF/MIN/MAX/ABS 组合。

